to darken.

17:18.905 --> 17:21.573
It ain't never
gonna darken!

17:23.844 --> 17:27.512
Ah, what you gonna do,
gonna cry about it?

17:27.514 --> 17:30.515
Huh?
You gon' cry about it, baby?

17:30.517 --> 17:32.250
Huh?
