21:16.811 --> 21:18.610
Huh?

21:18.612 --> 21:21.145
You stealing from me?

21:21.147 --> 21:23.148
Hmm?

21:23.150 --> 21:25.017
You gonna respect me
like that?

21:25.019 --> 21:28.153
Huh?

21:28.155 --> 21:29.754
Huh?!

21:29.756 --> 21:32.157
Don't lie to me.

21:35.830 --> 21:38.296
How dare you.

21:38.298 --> 21:42.300
How dare you come into my stuff
after all I done.

21:42.302 --> 21:44.302
Okay, how dare you.

21:44.304 --> 21:45.838
Now come on.
Gimme that back.

21:45.840 --> 21:47.039
That ain't yours.
Give it to me.

21:47.041 --> 21:48.440
Give it to me!
-Goddamn it!

21:48.442 --> 21:51.410
Mama, I will go to the police.
I will.

21:52.646 --> 21:54.979
Yeah,
you would, too, huh?

21:54.981 --> 21:56.248
-Mama...
-Stupid.

21:56.250 --> 21:59.651
You stupid. That's what you are.
You stupid.

21:59.653 --> 22:02.154
Mama,
please tell me.

22:11.866 --> 22:14.199
Fine, you want to know?

22:14.201 --> 22:17.269
You want to know?
I'll tell you.

22:17.271 --> 22:20.072
I always hated that name.
Fauna.

22:20.074 --> 22:25.444
It's like a stupid --
stupid fairy -- fairy-tale name.

22:27.682 --> 22:29.882
What?

22:32.687 --> 22:34.887
You...

22:37.424 --> 22:42.026
You -- you Fauna Hodel,
stupid, you are.

22:42.028 --> 22:44.330
You're Fauna.

22:46.233 --> 22:48.433
I am?

22:48.435 --> 22:51.537
Yeah, you was given to me
in a goddamn bathroom.

22:55.242 --> 23:00.312
White woman in the restroom
at a casino.

23:02.449 --> 23:06.651
Lonely, talking my damn ear off,
so, you know,

23:06.653 --> 23:11.189
I tell her about me
and the good Reverend Greenwade.

23:11.191 --> 23:12.925
Yeah,
I tell her we was married.

23:12.927 --> 23:17.996
You know, she was a big tipper,
so I laid it on thick.

23:17.998 --> 23:20.899
Says "Lord didn't bless us
with no children."

23:22.803 --> 23:25.938
She asked me if I would
adopt her daughter's child.

23:28.408 --> 23:31.876
I thought
she was drunk, crazy.

23:31.878 --> 23:34.546
I mean, who would've
thought she wasn't?

23:37.618 --> 23:39.351
So...

23:39.353 --> 23:43.922
I says, uh, "Wonderful, ma'am."
[ Laughs ]

23:46.360 --> 23:48.761
She tipped me $50.

23:51.432 --> 23:53.898
Her 15-year-old daughter,
that's --

23:53.900 --> 23:57.101
Go on, open it now.
That's the Tamar right there.

23:57.103 --> 24:01.105
Another stupid name.

24:01.107 --> 24:05.043
Pregnant by a Negro boy.

24:05.045 --> 24:07.512
Here I am --

24:07.514 --> 24:11.516
childless,
married to a preacher,

24:11.518 --> 24:14.586
decent Negro
God-fearing woman.

24:14.588 --> 24:16.321
So, she asked me
if I would take that baby.

24:16.323 --> 24:19.992
Shit, I said, "Praise Jesus,"
and she tipped me another $50.

24:23.063 --> 24:25.597
So, I get this --
I get this -- this telegram

24:25.599 --> 24:27.065
about six months on,

24:27.067 --> 24:28.533
and I didn't know what it was,
what to make of it.

24:28.535 --> 24:31.670
So, I threw the damn thing
in the trash.

24:31.672 --> 24:32.871
Shit.

24:32.873 --> 24:37.342
Now here comes
this white lady, okay,

24:37.344 --> 24:39.544
you know, on the floor,

24:39.546 --> 24:43.415
hollering about
keeping my word.

24:43.417 --> 24:44.616
You know?

24:44.618 --> 24:46.951
Making a scene,
about to get me fired.

24:46.953 --> 24:49.888
And she bring that baby
up here to Sisters.

24:49.890 --> 24:51.223
Well, then she meets
Christopher.

24:51.225 --> 24:52.825
Now Christopher's
seen the baby.

24:52.827 --> 24:54.759
Now Christopher says, "I -- you
know, we should keep the baby."

24:54.761 --> 24:56.495
He thinks it's gon' --
gon' settle me down,

24:56.497 --> 24:57.562
make us a damn family.

24:57.564 --> 24:59.898
Well, here we are.

24:59.900 --> 25:03.101
[ Laughs ]

25:03.103 --> 25:04.636
Here we are,

25:04.638 --> 25:07.906
without the good
Reverend Greenwade, of course.

25:07.908 --> 25:10.275
Asshole.

25:19.986 --> 25:22.588
You know I did
the best I could.

25:25.792 --> 25:30.262
You was always
the best-dressed girl in school.

25:30.264 --> 25:33.632
You always had
the best clothes.

25:40.541 --> 25:42.307
[ Sniffing ]

25:44.745 --> 25:47.012
I'm gonna be late.

25:51.886 --> 25:55.687
But you know this --
this is the important thing.

25:55.689 --> 25:57.890
Okay, you look at me.

25:57.892 --> 26:00.425
Your white family?

26:00.427 --> 26:02.627
They rich.

26:02.629 --> 26:06.631
Okay, your -- your --
your grandfather,

26:06.633 --> 26:10.635
he a famous doctor
in Los Angeles.

26:10.637 --> 26:13.705
You gonna be rich one day,
okay?

26:13.707 --> 26:15.908
So, you keep that name.
You keep that name legal.

26:15.910 --> 26:17.976
Fauna Hodel.

26:17.978 --> 26:23.848
♪♪

26:23.850 --> 26:28.454
That's why you don't need
no Lewis Ferguson.

26:31.058 --> 26:35.260
Now go and get dressed
for school.

26:35.262 --> 26:38.063
Don't be late.

