33:31.712 --> 33:34.513
What the hell
is wrong with m--

33:34.515 --> 33:37.116
-What the hell?
-[ Laughs ]

33:37.118 --> 33:40.251
I'm feeling a lot better,
Doc.

33:40.253 --> 33:42.053
-Come here!
-[ Laughs ]

33:42.055 --> 33:43.989
-Funny guy.
-Come on.

33:43.991 --> 33:46.792
-Get up!
-Get him out of here.

33:47.795 --> 33:50.195
Come on.
I don't know who you work for,

33:50.197 --> 33:52.131
but that's
illegal trespassing.

33:52.133 --> 33:55.200
Shit,
I bet there's tampering.

33:55.202 --> 33:57.336
-Come on, that's --
-And littering!

33:57.338 --> 33:59.671
-Yeah.
-Jackass.

33:59.673 --> 34:03.175
-Yeah, littering.
-Hey, genius.

34:05.078 --> 34:08.180
[ Laughs, coughs ]

34:10.351 --> 34:13.719
[ Grunts, laughs ]

34:18.759 --> 34:22.061
[ Grunting ]

34:27.701 --> 34:30.435
Ahh!

34:30.437 --> 34:33.105
Keep Calvin company.

34:35.042 --> 34:37.642
Hey, um, are you Calvin?

34:37.644 --> 34:38.910
Yeah.

34:38.912 --> 34:40.179
Yeah, they wanted me to --

34:40.181 --> 34:42.581
to see if you, uh,
needed anything.

34:42.583 --> 34:44.049
-I'm good, man.
-Yeah.

34:44.051 --> 34:46.919
-I'm great.
-I'll get off your legs now.

34:52.593 --> 34:54.325
-Lewis. Lewis!
-Yeah.

34:54.327 --> 34:56.595
You got any nickels,
dimes, anything?

34:56.597 --> 34:58.063
Yeah, I think so.
Why?

34:58.065 --> 34:59.931
Just give it to me.

34:59.933 --> 35:01.132
Sister Sarah:
About an hour ago.

35:01.134 --> 35:03.402
Please, could you check
downstairs?

35:03.404 --> 35:04.469
Thank you.

35:04.471 --> 35:05.871
Oh, Lewis?

35:05.873 --> 35:07.138
Yes, ma'am?

35:07.140 --> 35:08.339
Have you
seen Pat anywhere?

35:08.341 --> 35:10.141
No, ma'am,
not in a minute.

35:10.143 --> 35:12.411
Well, if you see her, tell her
to see me at once, please.

35:12.413 --> 35:14.780
Yes, ma'am.

35:18.886 --> 35:21.120
What the hell is going on,
Pat?

35:27.828 --> 35:29.762
♪♪

