35:41.642 --> 35:49.448
[<i> Line ringing</i> ]

35:53.454 --> 35:55.720
Hodel:<i> Hello?</i>

35:55.722 --> 35:58.857
<i> Hello?</i>

35:58.859 --> 36:02.394
-Mr. Hodel?
<i> -Who is this?</i>

36:02.396 --> 36:05.196
Mr. Hodel, um...

36:05.198 --> 36:06.732
It's Pat.
<i> -Pat, I'm sorry.</i>

36:06.734 --> 36:09.400
<i> I think you've got the wrong</i>
<i> number, and it's Doctor.</i>

36:09.402 --> 36:11.670
It's Fauna.

36:11.672 --> 36:15.040
Mr. -- Dr. Hodel...

36:17.078 --> 36:21.012
Tamar's daughter.

36:21.014 --> 36:23.248
Your granddaughter,
sir.

36:26.419 --> 36:28.087
<i> Fauna.</i>

36:29.423 --> 36:31.222
<i> Hello, Fauna.</i>

36:31.224 --> 36:33.492
<i> Nice to hear from you.</i>

36:33.494 --> 36:36.227
<i> Where are you?</i>

36:36.229 --> 36:38.630
-I'm in Sparks, sir.
<i> -Of course.</i>

36:38.632 --> 36:41.300
<i> Sparks. Of course.</i>

36:41.302 --> 36:43.936
<i> And things are well there?</i>

36:46.774 --> 36:50.109
Yes, I-I guess.

36:50.111 --> 36:53.879
<i> Has Mrs. Greenwade been</i>
<i> taking good care of you?</i>

36:56.450 --> 36:58.049
Fine, I guess.

36:58.051 --> 37:01.853
<i> Good. Good.</i>

37:01.855 --> 37:04.189
<i> Have you spoken to Tamar?</i>

37:06.193 --> 37:07.526
N-No, I-I didn't.

37:07.528 --> 37:11.262
<i> Good, good.</i>
<i> That's for the best.</i>

37:11.264 --> 37:14.466
<i> Your mother, sadly,</i>
<i> is not well.</i>

37:14.468 --> 37:16.267
<i> Not at all.</i>

37:16.269 --> 37:18.470
<i> I wouldn't talk to her</i>
<i> if I were you.</i>

37:18.472 --> 37:23.675
<i> It would be very distressing</i>
<i> and confusing.</i>

37:23.677 --> 37:26.211
<i> But it's lovely to hear</i>
<i> your voice, Fauna.</i>

37:26.213 --> 37:29.414
<i> I'm so glad</i>
<i> you've contacted me.</i>

37:29.416 --> 37:32.017
<i> In fact, you should come here</i>
<i> and see me.</i>

37:32.019 --> 37:34.553
<i> Would you like that?</i>

37:34.555 --> 37:37.956
-Yes, sir, I would.
<i> -Wonderful.</i>

37:37.958 --> 37:41.360
<i> Call me when you arrive.</i>

37:41.362 --> 37:42.293
<i> Goodbye now.</i>

37:42.295 --> 37:43.762
[<i> Receiver clicks</i> ]

37:43.764 --> 37:46.498
Pat!

37:46.500 --> 37:48.367
Pat.

37:48.369 --> 37:50.235
Yes, Sister Sarah,
I'm sorry.

37:50.237 --> 37:51.770
I shouldn't have done that.
-I am so sorry, child.

37:51.772 --> 37:53.038
I'm sorry you have to
bear this burden.

37:53.040 --> 37:54.239
No, I should've asked.
I'm sorry.

37:54.241 --> 37:55.974
Pat! Listen to me.

37:55.976 --> 37:58.577
It's your mother.
-My mother?

37:58.579 --> 38:00.979
Mama?
-I'm so sorry.

38:00.981 --> 38:02.848
Your mother's passed.

38:02.850 --> 38:05.650
She's been called.

38:05.652 --> 38:08.187
-What?
-Your mother is dead, child.

38:08.189 --> 38:11.990
Jimmy Lee's gone to God.
The police called.

38:11.992 --> 38:13.993
It's okay.
Let us pray.

38:13.995 --> 38:15.194
Let's say
the Lord's Prayer.

38:15.196 --> 38:17.363
Our Father,
who art --

38:19.400 --> 38:20.933
Pat.

38:25.606 --> 38:28.440
♪♪

38:31.912 --> 38:34.446
Mama?

38:34.448 --> 38:36.382
Mama!

38:38.385 --> 38:40.853
Mama!

38:41.988 --> 38:43.856
Ma--

38:45.926 --> 38:49.994
