38:50.597 --> 38:53.598
Jimmy Lee:
That's why the car don't work.

38:53.600 --> 38:56.201
Everything I'm supposed
to be doing.

38:56.203 --> 38:57.736
Homer: Jimmy Lee, look.

38:57.738 --> 38:59.137
Man: She's more screwed up
than that screwdriver.

38:59.139 --> 39:00.805
Look, damn it.

39:00.807 --> 39:02.607
Didn't I tell you I'd get her
here lickety split?

39:02.609 --> 39:05.878
-Shit.
-Can't believe you did that.

39:05.880 --> 39:08.881
