50:07.375 --> 50:10.108
[ Telephone ringing ]

50:10.110 --> 50:12.011
[ Grunts ]

50:15.515 --> 50:17.683
[ Groans ]

50:25.459 --> 50:26.925
Yeah?

50:26.927 --> 50:29.595
Jimmy Lee:<i> Yeah, is this,</i>
<i> um, Jay Singletary,</i>

50:29.597 --> 50:31.329
<i> the -- the reporter?</i>

50:31.331 --> 50:33.732
<i> Yes, who -- who is it?</i>

50:33.734 --> 50:35.734
Yeah, y-you the one
that wrote that, uh,

50:35.736 --> 50:38.270
article for the
<i> Los Angeles Examiner</i>

50:38.272 --> 50:40.672
about Dr. George Hodel?

50:40.674 --> 50:42.675
<i> In '49?</i>

50:44.945 --> 50:46.478
<i> You there?</i>

50:46.480 --> 50:49.147
Uh, [Clears throat]
yeah, yeah.

50:49.149 --> 50:51.749
George Hodel, yes.

50:51.751 --> 50:53.018
Look...

50:53.020 --> 50:56.154
<i> you were right about him.</i>
<i> You got to keep looking.</i>

50:56.156 --> 50:59.291
Y-- Hello --
What -- Who -- Hello?

50:59.293 --> 51:01.560
Hello? Hello?

51:05.165 --> 51:07.966
Dr. George Hodel.

51:07.968 --> 51:10.636
♪♪

51:15.042 --> 51:18.978
♪♪

51:22.049 --> 51:25.583
[<i> Line ringing</i> ]

51:25.585 --> 51:27.385
<i> -Hello?</i>
-Yes, hello.

51:27.387 --> 51:29.387
This is Fauna Hodel again.

51:29.389 --> 51:31.657
I'm George's granddaughter.

51:31.659 --> 51:33.459
Woman:<i> Mm-hmm.</i>

51:33.461 --> 51:35.393
Listen, I know I already
called twice,

51:35.395 --> 51:38.530
but is Dr. Hodel there?

51:38.532 --> 51:40.866
<i> No, he's not here.</i>
<i> I'll take a message.</i>

51:40.868 --> 51:43.401
<i> Thank you, yes.</i>
<i> The message is from Fauna.</i>

51:43.403 --> 51:44.803
<i> -Mm-hmm.</i>
<i> -And I'm in Los Angeles.</i>

51:44.805 --> 51:47.272
I'm at the downtown
Greyhound station.

51:47.274 --> 51:48.606
<i> I'll let him know.</i>

51:48.608 --> 51:50.876
<i> Thank you, ma'am.</i>

51:50.878 --> 51:53.812
♪♪

51:56.016 --> 51:58.984
♪♪

52:00.821 --> 52:06.291
<i> Hello, um, is this, uh --</i>
<i> is this Corinna Hodel?</i>

52:06.293 --> 52:10.362
<i> -Who's calling?</i>
-Mrs. Hodel, this is Fauna.

52:10.364 --> 52:11.963
<i> Fauna Hodel.</i>

52:11.965 --> 52:15.767
<i> I -- I believe</i>
<i> I'm your step-granddaughter.</i>

52:15.769 --> 52:17.569
<i> Please, ma'am,</i>
<i> I-I-I'm sorry to bother you,</i>

52:17.571 --> 52:19.237
<i> but, you know,</i>
<i> Dr. George Hodel,</i>

52:19.239 --> 52:22.574
<i> he invited me to Los Angeles</i>
<i> to come visit, and...</i>

52:22.576 --> 52:24.910
<i> I can't seem to reach him,</i>
<i> so maybe you --</i>

52:24.912 --> 52:28.313
You listen to me now.

52:28.315 --> 52:29.781
Your grandfather...

52:29.783 --> 52:36.054
he's a very,
very dangerous man.

52:36.056 --> 52:38.190
Stay away.

52:38.192 --> 52:40.926
Stay away from him.

52:40.928 --> 52:44.062
<i> Far, far away.</i>

52:44.064 --> 52:46.598
[<i> Receiver clicks</i> ]

52:46.600 --> 52:49.635
♪♪

52:55.675 --> 52:59.545
Your granddaughter
called.

52:59.547 --> 53:01.947
I'll take care of it.

